snippet.title: Minecraft x Walt Disney Magic Kingdom DLC: Official Trailer
snippet.description: The happiest place on Earth comes to the Overworld! In honor of the 50th anniversary of Walt Disney World, the Magic Kingdom has been faithfully recreated in Minecraft. Featuring thrilling rides, iconic Disney and Pixar characters, and skins to help you dress the part! Get the DLC now at Minecraft.net/marketplace
